# 1Ô∏è‚É£6Ô∏è‚É£ GOVERNANCE CONTROLS

Logic 24 enforces:

* Mandatory design validation before publication
* Audit log of revisions (Logic 14)
* Justification record for overridden warnings
* Compliance review for critical bias flags

Integrated with:

* Logic 8 ‚Üí Evaluation design
* Logic 21 ‚Üí Market participation analytics
* Logic 22 ‚Üí Capacity feasibility
* Logic 23 ‚Üí Anti-collusion ecosystem protection

