Prevents:

‚ùå Supplier-specific tender tailoring
‚ùå Accidental exclusion of SMEs
‚ùå Ambiguous scope disputes
‚ùå Unrealistic delivery requirements
‚ùå Structural scoring manipulation
‚ùå Re-tendering cycles due to design flaws

